# App version & changelog

Version and release notes live in:

- `src/version.ts` — `APP_VERSION` (semver, e.g. `0.0.1`)
- `src/changelog.ts` — `CHANGELOG` array (newest first)

**Do not** bump the version or update the changelog automatically after changes.

Only update version and changelog when the user **explicitly asks** (e.g. «обнови версию», «добавь в чейнджлог», «релиз»).

When asked:

1. Bump the **patch** segment in `src/version.ts`.
2. Keep `package.json` `"version"` in sync with `APP_VERSION`.
3. Prepend a new entry to `CHANGELOG` with `version`, `date` (`YYYY-MM-DD`), and `changes.ru` / `changes.en` bullets summarizing what shipped since the last release.
